52:50.880 --> 52:53.040
DANIEL: Barcelona?
HELEN: Yes.

52:57.640 --> 52:59.360
DANIEL: Why Barcelona?

53:01.280 --> 53:03.560
We used to watch them together.

53:04.440 --> 53:05.960
He liked Messi.

53:07.960 --> 53:09.480
Something Messi.

53:09.560 --> 53:11.000
Lionel Messi.

53:15.200 --> 53:18.320
Yes. I know you like Messi, Vernon,
I've seen your room.

53:20.560 --> 53:23.960
If there's a shred of comfort
I can take from this,

53:24.040 --> 53:27.160
it's that deep down
I'm glad God took him before me.

53:30.600 --> 53:31.680
Why?

53:32.960 --> 53:36.000
The number of sleepless nights
I had worried about

53:36.080 --> 53:39.640
what would become of him
if anything ever happened to me.

53:42.400 --> 53:43.880
He was such a kind and loving boy,

53:43.960 --> 53:47.760
but when he was having
one of his episodes, he was so...

53:49.840 --> 53:51.160
Difficult.

53:51.960 --> 53:54.040
I knew, no matter how hard I prayed,

53:54.120 --> 53:56.880
the chances of him ever leading
a normal life were slim.

53:58.600 --> 54:00.720
I worried about him growing old.

54:02.120 --> 54:05.400
The thought of him ending up
in some institution,

54:05.480 --> 54:08.080
with nobody in the world to love him.

54:12.120 --> 54:14.320
Brenda understood how I felt.

54:15.520 --> 54:17.000
Carl's mother.

54:18.920 --> 54:22.320
We both had sons who were
troubled in their own ways.

54:23.520 --> 54:25.880
That's why we felt such affinity.

54:30.360 --> 54:31.440
Yes?

54:34.000 --> 54:36.120
DANIEL: This is unfair.

54:36.200 --> 54:37.680
What is unfair?

54:38.400 --> 54:40.360
I cannot argue with you.

54:41.280 --> 54:43.800
I cannot contradict you
in these circumstances.

54:43.880 --> 54:45.120
Why not?

54:46.040 --> 54:48.440
You have done nothing but contradict me

54:48.520 --> 54:51.880
since the moment you arrived.
So why stop now?

54:51.960 --> 54:54.080
Because he home?

54:54.160 --> 54:57.040
Is he more dead now than he was before?

54:57.120 --> 54:59.560
More dead now that you can see him?

55:00.040 --> 55:03.880
Her son and mine both had
difficulties growing up.

55:05.160 --> 55:07.840
Were both picked on
because they were different,

55:07.920 --> 55:10.440
and we bonded because of it.

55:11.360 --> 55:13.240
Because they were so alike.

55:14.960 --> 55:17.600
When Brenda was diagnosed,

55:17.680 --> 55:21.160
she came to me, worried about
what would become of Carl.

55:22.400 --> 55:25.720
I promised her that I would always
keep an eye out for her

55:25.800 --> 55:27.960
and I intend to keep that promise.

55:28.800 --> 55:30.360
She was a good mother

55:30.440 --> 55:32.640
who never once tried to change him,

55:32.720 --> 55:36.480
but accepted him for who he was,
and I so admired her for that.

55:38.080 --> 55:42.840
Her love was unconditional
and that's exactly how it should be.

55:46.640 --> 55:47.800
Daniel...

55:50.200 --> 55:55.440
I wouldn't care if my son was straight,

55:55.520 --> 55:57.520
gay or anything else,

55:57.600 --> 56:01.480
just so long as I can see that
beautiful smile once more.

56:15.000 --> 56:16.760
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

56:19.040 --> 56:20.200
I'll get that.

56:27.280 --> 56:29.280
Can I speak to Helen, please?

56:30.640 --> 56:31.680
Yeah, come in.

56:35.080 --> 56:36.960
Look, it's fine. Honest.

56:55.280 --> 56:56.960
I knew you'd have him in that shirt.

57:01.800 --> 57:04.120
I'm stopping all this right now.

57:05.160 --> 57:09.520
I'm telling them whatever I need
to tell them to get it all to stop.

57:09.960 --> 57:11.280
HELEN: Thank you.

57:12.160 --> 57:13.960
I'm not doing it for him.

57:15.000 --> 57:16.440
I'm doing it for you.

57:17.560 --> 57:19.080
And for Vernon.

57:23.280 --> 57:25.720
Brenda would be so proud of you.

57:28.400 --> 57:29.520
Yeah.

57:37.440 --> 57:38.440
[DOOR CLOSES]

57:39.200 --> 57:40.440
Praise the Lord.

57:49.400 --> 57:51.280
There's more Christianity
in your little finger

57:51.360 --> 57:53.400
than in that man's entire body.

57:53.480 --> 57:56.680
Yeah?
Why don't you tell that to your bishop.

57:56.760 --> 57:58.200
Tell it to your Pope.

57:58.280 --> 58:00.680
Shout it from the rooftops,
why don't you?

58:00.760 --> 58:02.760
